<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><?Xpress productLine="ncc-clause"?><clause id="_d71a9cd2-d7f8-46fe-9c55-29094b04e664" outputclass="ncc-clause" variation="TAS"><meta><facet building="Class 1a"/><facet building="Class 1b"/><facet building="Class 10a"/><facet building="Class 10b"/><facet building="Class 10c"/></meta><sptc>I12D5</sptc><title id="_7bc20b99-5ced-4b90-957f-8691e384a330">Required exits</title><archive-num>2019: TAS H114.5</archive-num><subclause id="_16003cbd-048a-4c12-a4ab-e90414ac4d91" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_d0312f9e-f684-4136-bb00-c396321779ac">SubClause</title><num>1</num><p>Each fire-separated section of a building which is a work place must have at least two <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1263_2.3.0.xml#_9712f630-8cf7-401b-b1cc-ae0be4485915" id="_128c3380-bc13-4623-8ba7-34aa7c811aa6" inv:access="external" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">exits</xref> for escape purposes and the number and location of <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1263_2.3.0.xml#_9712f630-8cf7-401b-b1cc-ae0be4485915" id="_ff9a8221-c24a-431a-8bfc-339dfba60de8" inv:access="external" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">exits</xref> must be such that any point on the floor is not further than 20 m from one of the <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1263_2.3.0.xml#_9712f630-8cf7-401b-b1cc-ae0be4485915" id="_085754b0-4875-4db9-bef3-b31ca80559f0" inv:access="external" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">exits</xref>.</p></subclause><subclause id="_16760698-1ed4-4cbd-a8c5-662446fb90a5" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_b8b71390-657d-45e5-9e3f-1559b457e793">SubClause</title><num>2</num><p>Only <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1263_2.3.0.xml#_9712f630-8cf7-401b-b1cc-ae0be4485915" id="_5efd0674-ecff-438a-95b0-d52b65711302" inv:access="external" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">exits</xref> with vertically hinged swinging doors may be considered as <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1263_2.3.0.xml#_9712f630-8cf7-401b-b1cc-ae0be4485915" id="_e52ae411-458d-4cfc-9348-f4dcf64ab3e2" inv:access="external" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">exits</xref> for the purposes of this clause.</p></subclause></clause>